WEBVTT

31:56.830 --> 31:58.200 line:80%
My dearest Song Yan

31:58.390 --> 32:00.070 line:80%
just wanted to prioritize his studies.

32:00.070 --> 32:01.470 line:80%
Prioritize his studies?

32:02.720 --> 32:05.960 line:80%
When you made a promise to
the Fan family ten years ago,

32:05.960 --> 32:07.630 line:80%
your excuse was also to
prioritize your studies.
